The paper discusses the design of a low dropout voltage regulator for use in cellular handsets, which involves aspects of electrical engineering and circuit design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.ET (Electronics and Electrical Engineering). Other possible categories include cs.CE (Circuit Design), cs.EM (Electromagnetics), cs.MM (Microelectronics), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
